snippet.title: The Real Reason Why Amber Heard is Lying
snippet.description:
The Real Reason Why Amber Heard is Lying

Is Amber Heard lying? This is the question that has caused a lot of controversies lately. There has been plenty of evidence by Johnny's team proving that Amber has started fights and hit him before but there is no direct evidence Johnny did the same actions. Even Amber's parents stand by Johnny deep down. Enjoy watching and don't forget to smash that Like button at the end.
